      "span_text": "It has been reported that functionalization of NPs with AMPs overcomes problems such as proteolytic degradation and peptide self-aggregation, maintaining their antimicrobial properties. We found that the membrane surface was not significantly modified after treatment with AuNPs-indolicidin, as shown by ZP experiments."
